A very lightweight Bitcoin crypto library for use with Android or any normal JVM-based project.  A portion of the library contains code from [Bouncy Castle](http://www.bouncycastle.org).

This product is licensed commercially however the author claims the source will be released into the public domain (UNLICENSE) at a future date (1.1).

